channel.title: Farcasting+Magic Accuracy
channel.description:
Im currently using a pwnscape source, and the autocasting on it is a little buggy.
The problem is that when you set autocast up, it will be very delayed, that is even if it works.
Half of the time the autocast wont work and you have to set it up multiple times, and magic is very inaccurate, and i was wondering if there was a way to change the rate at which magic hits and freezes if using ice spells.
Sorry im new to coding, and my friend that was helping me learn, and helping me with the server is on vacation so im trying to get some stuff done by myself.
